    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/b53e1a492d5cf46aca84f41e799c22be.poster.avif?t=1688677587\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/b53e1a492d5cf46aca84f41e799c22be.webm?t=1688677587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/b53e1a492d5cf46aca84f41e799c22be.mp4?t=1688677587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Polestar is a classic Turn-Based RPG set in a fantasy-western world.  Boasting a unique hand-drawn style, you'll battle enemies with Timed-Hits to delay their attacks, decide between keeping equipment or breaking it down to harness it's latent abilities, and decipher the mysterious insignia that seems to be following our hero, Hale, across the continent of Graydon.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/7c8c34010fbfa3d1fbf1393097390d7e.poster.avif?t=1688677587\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/7c8c34010fbfa3d1fbf1393097390d7e.webm?t=1688677587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/7c8c34010fbfa3d1fbf1393097390d7e.mp4?t=1688677587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/3f21b39e319fc0464db7660f82a3aa14.avif?t=1688677587\" width=616 height=74 /></span><br><br>Dive into a fully illustrated world inspired by classic japanese role playing games of days long gone! Investigate the painted landscapes with 2D animated characters while traversing the vast sun-kissed deserts, beautiful coasts and decaying waterways of the world of Polestar.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/43d155e3d4ea3d00097e4f92f335882b.poster.avif?t=1688677587\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/43d155e3d4ea3d00097e4f92f335882b.webm?t=1688677587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/43d155e3d4ea3d00097e4f92f335882b.mp4?t=1688677587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/4f35cee9e0e86be3c95163cfeeb9b237.avif?t=1688677587\" width=616 height=74 /></span><br><br>A modern twist on the traditional Active Time Battle system offering the ability to disrupt enemy attacks with devastating Timed-Hits.  Battle against a diverse array of ridiculous enemies, frightening foes and threatening bosses!  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/01972cf3e854fdbcdd4dab747843cc66.poster.avif?t=1688677587\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/01972cf3e854fdbcdd4dab747843cc66.webm?t=1688677587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/01972cf3e854fdbcdd4dab747843cc66.mp4?t=1688677587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/f9f4afed24c1f527a19055e4d23af18c.avif?t=1688677587\" width=616 height=74 /></span><br><br>Saloons, Locomotives, Wanted Posters and Stoats. Polestar is a world overlooking a precipice of change. From cowtowns like Haevstock, looking back on it’s golden years with mournful eyes, to Beckbrum, a dazzling city filled with new technology and illicit undetones – There’s plenty of room for misadventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/a0e033cc09ef3c0f7093d2bdc181f822.poster.avif?t=1688677587\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/a0e033cc09ef3c0f7093d2bdc181f822.webm?t=1688677587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/a0e033cc09ef3c0f7093d2bdc181f822.mp4?t=1688677587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132220/extras/dd6c0a82a949dad1cc67d8228f02c558.avif?t=1688677587\" width=616 height=74 /></span><br><br>Join our protagonist Hale on his journey and meet a wild ensemble of characters. From sleazy merchants and notable thieves to murderous bounty hunters and worst of all - government officials.",
